Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:23.32,OP Ro,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}wakachiau koi ni ikisaki wo terase
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:27.96,OP Ro,,0000,0000,0000,,kakumei wo! let's shout {\fad(150,150)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:32.74,OP Ro,,0000,0000,0000,,kakumei wo! let's shout {\fad(150,150)}
