Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:09.50,OP Ro,,0000,0000,0000,,futtou seyo ishiki no rei {\fad(150,150)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.19,OP Ro,,0000,0000,0000,,kyuusaku suru flash naru you ni {\fad(150,150)}
